<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idab7be491-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective 120 days after <date date="2000-10-30">Oct. 30, 2000</date>, see section 1 [[div. A], title X, § 1090(c)] of <ref href="/us/pl/106/398">Pub. L. 106–398</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s9491">section 9491 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
